## Brief Synthesis Workflow

Transform fragmented inputs into a complete brief:

- [ ] 1. Gather inputs: Collect all source materials (emails, call notes, brief docs)
- [ ] 2. Identify gaps: Note what information is missing or unclear
- [ ] 3. Stakeholder alignment: Clarify objectives with the client if needed
- [ ] 4. Synthesize: Combine all inputs into a structured brief format
- [ ] 5. Validate: Confirm brief is complete and accurate with client
- [ ] 6. Distribute: Share final brief with execution team

